# Dark Mode & Themes - Professional UI Adaptation

## 1. Understanding Color Schemes (45 min)

### System Color Schemes
iOS provides two main appearance modes:
- **Light Mode**: Bright interface with dark text
- **Dark Mode**: Dark interface with light text
- **Automatic**: Follows system setting

### Color Assets in Xcode
Organize colors in Asset Catalog for better management:
```swift
