Color.secondary      // Adapts between dark/light gray
Color.backgroundColor // System background color
```

## 2. Implementing Adaptive Colors (60 min)

### Creating Adaptive Color Assets
1. **Add Color Set** in Assets.xcassets
2. **Define Both Appearances**: Light & Dark variants
3. **Use Any/Any Appearance** for universal compatibility

### Programmatic Color Creation
```swift
